These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, zinnia, bellflower, orchid
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
4 different games are played: go, snooker, domino, scrabble
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, ebony, emerald
House: farmhouse, colonial, palace, tower
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, fonseca, blend, bluemaster
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the person who growsbegonia and the person who likes ivory##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the colonial house##1
 5. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who likes emerald##2
 8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person playing go##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the fan of electronic##1
10. the colonial house is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the tower house is the person playing domino##1
12. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
13. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the palace house##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Flower      | bellflower        | orchid     | zinnia | begonia      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Game         | snooker  | scrabble    | go       | domino     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Color           | ebony    | ivory | chestnut      | emerald     |
| House         | farmhouse   | colonial   | palace      | tower    |
| Cigar     | vegafina        | fonseca        | bluemaster    | blend    |

