 9. the person playing poker is the aprilerman##1
10. the indian is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the paramedic is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
12. the indian is between the person playing snooker and the indonesian##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
14. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
